      p ∈ convexHull ℝ (x '' I) ∧ p ∈ convexHull ℝ (x '' J) := by
    -- This is a standard consequence of the fact that 4 points in ℝ² are affinely dependent.
    -- Radon's theorem is typically found in Mathlib.Analysis.Convex.Radon.
